<li>[ ] Keyword density between 0.8% and 1.2%</li>
<li>[ ] Original examples added (not generic)</li>
<li>[ ] Tone matches brand voice</li>
<li>[ ] Sentences under 20 words</li>
<li>[ ] Paragraphs under 3 sentences</li>
<li>[ ] Internal links to 2-3 related articles</li>
<li>[ ] External links to 2-3 authoritative sources</li>
<li>[ ] Meta title under 60 characters</li>
<li>[ ] Meta description under 160 characters with keyword</li>
</ul>
